definition: tree/wood/coffin/wooden/simple/numb/one of the eight categories of ancient musical instruments 八音[ba1 yin1]

sentences.english: More tall and stately that the alder.
sentences.chinese: 你比榿木還要高挑和端莊。

sentences.english: During the winter, the male inflorescences of Alnus mandshurica and Alnus sibirica were naked.
sentences.chinese: 東北榿木和遼東榿木的雄花序均裸露越冬。

sentences.english: During the winter, the male inflorescences of Alnus mandshurica and Alnus sibirica were naked.

sentences.english: Cedar or alder are traditional, but maple is nice too.
sentences.chinese: 雪松或榿木是傳統的，但楓是太漂亮。
